properties.Name: CustomerAction
properties.Description: A Customer Action that occurs or is recorded in connection with the customer.

Columns.Name: CustomerId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Customer.

Columns.Name: CustomerActionTypeId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Customer Action Type.

Columns.Name: CustomerActionTimestamp
Columns.Description: The timestamp of the customer action.

Columns.Name: CustomerActionValue
Columns.Description: A value associated with the customer action, normally as a result of the outcome of the action. It is possible that no value is associated with a particular action.

Columns.Name: CustomerActionNote
Columns.Description: A note, comment or additional information regarding the customer action.

Columns.Name: CustomerActionStatusId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Customer Account Event Status.

Columns.Name: SourcePartyId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Party.
